---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title='Animancy Designs.'>
	<main class='landing'>
		<header class='hero'>
			<Navbar />
			<div class='u-container'>
				<h1>Design with Soul.</h1>
				<div>
					<p>
						We Create the web for businesses, content creators, and art creatives. We are here to
						help you take the first steps to building an online presence that tells the world about
						your dream.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</header>

		<section class='process'>
			<div class='u-container flow-large'>
				<header>
					<h1>How we work.</h1>
				</header>
				<article class='process__content u-flex'>
					<div class='card flow'>
						<header>
							<h3>01. Strategy</h3>
						</header>
						<p>
							We first focus on getting to know about your dream and idea. Sitting with you, talking
							about content helps us to make some bid design decisions before getting to the
							visuals.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class='card flow'>
						<header>
							<h3>02. Design</h3>
						</header>
						<p>
							After gathering the content, we form a design. We conduct research based on the
							content and provide design mockups to narrow down the website you want.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class='card flow'>
						<header>
							<h3>03. Development</h3>
						</header>
						<p>
							After careful consideration, we create a website that meets your specs and
							incorporates all requested features, ideas, and concepts. We take pride in our work
							and ensure the highest quality and that your needs are fully met.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class='card flow'>
						<header>
							<h3>04. Support & Assistance</h3>
						</header>
						<p>
							Lastly, we sit down and talk about how to use your website, such as how to go about
							updating the website, or helping to plan a launch date that works within your favor.
						</p>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id='services' class='services'>
			<div class='u-container flow-large'>
				<header>
					<h1>What we can do.</h1>
				</header>
				<article class='flow-large'>
					<div class='detail flow'>
						<header>
							<h3>Web Design and Development</h3>
						</header>
						<p>
							We create the web using the right tools for the right job. Let us create an online
							presence for you, that will take you to the next level, allowing you to take your
							steps with what you are passionate about.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class='detail flow'>
						<header>
							<p>Coming Soon</p>
							<h3>OBS Graphics & Effects</h3>
						</header>
						<p>
							We use <a class='event-link' href='https://www.nodecg.dev/' target='_blank'>NodeCG</a>
							to create broadcast graphics. This service allows one to run complicated parts of their
							stream smoothly, and we also can provide subtle animations for sub alerts, and social media
							callouts.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class='detail flow'>
						<header>
							<h3>Data Integration</h3>
						</header>
						<p>
							If you want to display information, redeems, top cheer, etc. Animancy can integrate
							that data using the Twitch API.
						</p>
					</div>

					<hr class='daimond-hr' />
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
